commentTextItems.html: bowled! a googly from Kapali, which does not bounce and Fahad Alhasmi goes for a big heave and missed it completely, the ball crashes into the stumps.

commentPostTextItems.html: That's it Bangladesh win by 96 runs. Once Bangladesh reached 300, UAE really had no chance with the experience they had. It needed a real big effort in the beginning but they had early setbacks as they lost wickets. Khurram Khan played well for his 78 but it was not enough. Mohammad Ashraful picks up the Man-of-the-Match award for his wonderful knock of 109.
Thanks for being with us, do join us again tomorrow, until then this is Binoy George and along with Chaminda signing off.
"Viewers in the USA can watch ten-minute highlights packages of both innings by clicking here ESPN 360.. These will be available approximately four hours after the end of each innings."

milestones.description: Khurram Khan has become the top wicket-taker for UAE in ODIs with 7 wickets, going past Dukanwala's 6
Ashraful and Raqibul Hasan's 141-run partnership is BAN's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 134 between Nafees and Shakib
Arshad Ali and Khurram Khan's 47-run partnership is UAE's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 20 between Mohammad Ishaq and Saleem Raza
Khurram Khan has conceded the most runs in an innings (78) in ODIs for UAE, going past Zarawani's record of 69
